'''Geeridu''' sidoo kale loo yaqaano '''dhimasho''' ({{lang-en|death}}; {{lang-ar|موت}}) waa marka [[naf]]tu ka baxdo [[jidh]]ka [[noole]]. Sharaxaada [[Saynis]]ka ee geerida, sidoo kale loo yaqaano ''dhimasho'', waa dhamaadka [[dhimasho|shaqada bayoloji]] ee suurtagelisa [[nolol|nolosha]] walax nool. Taasi micnaheedu waa istaagayso wada shaqeynta xubnaha jidhka iyo wixii ku dhexjira. Sida caadiga ah dhimashada waxaa keena waxyaabo badan waxaana ugu caansan [[gabow]]ga, [[nafaqo]]darada, [[xanuun]]ada, isdilitaanka (suicide), xasuuqida ama dilka (homocide), [[gaajo|gaajada iyo baahida]], [[biyo]]la'aanta sidoo kale loo yaqaano [[haraad]]ka, [[shil]]ka, dhaawaca iyo wixii la halmaala.<ref>{{cite web|last=Zimmerman |first=Leda |title=Must all organisms age and die? |url=http://engineering.mit.edu/live/news/1223-must-all-organisms-age-and-die |publisher=Massachusetts Institute of Technology School of Engineering |accessdate=5 February 2012 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101101081710/http://engineering.mit.edu/live/news/1223-must-all-organisms-age-and-die |archivedate=1 November 2010 |date=19 October 2010 |deadurl=no}}</ref> 

Jidhka noolaha geeriyooday wuu qudhma isla wakhtiyar ka dib dhimashada, wuxuuna ku darsamaa [[caro|carada]]. Laakiin waxaa mudo dheer sii jira [[laf]]aha iyo [[ilig|ilkaha]] kuwaasi oo meelaha qaar la helo lafo ama ilko jira kumanaan sano.

Guud ahaan geeridu waa mid xaq ah, sida [[diin]]ta [[Islaam]]ka ah ku xusan qof walba sugaysa. Geeridu waa albaabka iyo wadada [[aakhiro|nolosha aakhiro]], waa mid lama huraan ah. 
Sidoo kale dhimashado waa arin murugo badan, naxdin, welwel, cabsi, iyo marooradilaac ku keenta [[qoys]]ka iyo [[qaraabo|qaraabada]] laga geeriyooday. Guud ahaana waa mid [[dad|aadamuhu]] neceb yahay.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.etymonline.com/index.php?term=death |title=Online Etymology Dictionary |work=[[Online Etymology Dictionary]] |accessdate=5 November 2013}}</ref> Waxaa taariikhda lagu sheegay in tirada dad ah ee dhimatay tan iyo biloowgii aadamaha ay ka badan tahay tirada maanta nool. Taas macnaheedu waa in dad ka badan 7 bilyan (dadka maanta ku nool aduunka) ay horey u geeriyoodeen.


